OL,3,CVolunteers win national award for
OL,4,C'lifeline' pay-as-you-feel cafe in Peel
OL,6,FA group of volunteers running a 'pay-
OL,7,Fas-you-feel' cafe in the west of the
OL,8,FIsle of Man have been awarded a
OL,9,Fnational award for their dedication to
OL,10,Fhelping those in need.
OL,12,FThe 'Big Table Cafe' was named
OL,13,F'Volunteer 'Volunteer Team of the
OL,14,FYear' by the Association of English
OL,15,FCathedrals, after providing lunches
OL,16,Fevery Monday for those in need living
OL,17,Fin and around the town of Peel.
