OL,4,C'lifeline' pay-as-you-feel cafe in Peel
OL,6,FThe 'eat what you like, pay what you
OL,7,Fcan' service gives customers the
OL,8,Fchoice to donate money anonymously for
OL,9,Ftheir meal, by handing in a sealed
OL,10,Fenvelope on their way out.
OL,12,FFenalla Costain is one of the
OL,13,Forganisers of the weekly cafe, and
OL,14,Fsaid: "If you can afford to pay for
OL,15,Fyour meal, then that's great, you put
OL,16,Fmoney in the envelope.
