OL,3,CVolunteers win national award for
OL,4,C'lifeline' pay-as-you-feel cafe in Peel
OL,6,F"If you can't afford it then you can
OL,7,Fhave a free meal - no questions asked,
OL,8,Fno stigma attached - we manage to make
OL,9,Fenough every week to cover our costs,
OL,10,Fand that's what it's about".
OL,12,FThe team cooks and prepares a three
OL,13,Fcourse meal every Monday, giving those
OL,14,Fwho are struggling access to fresh
OL,15,Ffood each week.
OL,17,FPeter Girdler, 89, arrives early every
OL,18,FMonday to prepare food, and says it
OL,19,F'gives him a purpose' each week.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
