OL,3,CVolunteers win national award for
OL,4,C'lifeline' pay-as-you-feel cafe in Peel
OL,6,FHe said: "I really enjoy it! When I
OL,7,Ffirst started if we got 30 people, we
OL,8,Fthought we were busy, and now we're
OL,9,Fdoubling that sometimes and way above
OL,10,Fit."
OL,12,FWhen asked how Peter felt about the
OL,13,Fteam winning the award, he said: "It
OL,14,Fwas quite a surprise that our little
OL,15,Ftiny place over here won an award of
OL,16,Fsuch status, because let's face it,
OL,17,Fthe cathedrals in England are massive!"
OL,19,FThe Dean, the Very Revd Nigel Godfrey,
OL,20,Fsaid, 'The Big Table Cafe is a life-
OL,21,Fline for so many.
