OL,3,CVolunteers win national award for
OL,4,C'lifeline' pay-as-you-feel cafe in Peel
OL,6,F'The volunteers give the impression
OL,7,Fthat nothing is too much trouble. They
OL,8,Fare meticulous in catering for a range
OL,9,Fof diets and coping with allergies and
OL,10,Fmaking the 60 or so customers from
OL,11,Fwhatever background welcome, and
OL,12,Fenabling them to also have take-away
OL,13,Fmeals for the coming week, especially
OL,14,Fthose who have limited means or
OL,15,Flimited catering facilities.
