OL,3,CVolunteers win national award for
OL,4,C'lifeline' pay-as-you-feel cafe in Peel
OL,6,F'The whole team is voluntary. There is
OL,7,Fa preparation team, a chef team, a
OL,8,Fwaiting-on team, and a washing-up
OL,9,Fteam. They all work well together and
OL,10,Fsupport each other, stepping in when
OL,11,Fthere are staff shortages in
OL,12,Fparticular areas.
OL,14,F'The project has been going for a
OL,15,Fnumber of years, its delivery service
OL,16,Fwas a lifeline in Covid and continues
OL,17,Fto provide a vital service for those
OL,18,Fin need,' he added.
OL,20,FThe 'Big Table Cafe' is open every
OL,21,Fweek on Mondays.
